review: Fabulous experience in the Witch's Lair. Don't miss it! We'll be back next month to try another room. Thank you!

room_title: Escape room "The Witch's Lair" by Human vs Room in Bethlehem
review: Just went to play the Witches Lair today with some friends. We had so much fun! The room was challenging, but not aggravating. The staff were super nice and extremely helpful. My friends and I will definitely be back very soon! Thanks to human vs room and their staff for the awesome experience!
